.TH CATNIP-REPL 1 "March 2026" "catnip-tools" "Catnip Language"
.SH NAME
catnip-repl \- interactive REPL for the Catnip language
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B catnip-repl
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B catnip-repl
is a terminal-based interactive Read-Eval-Print Loop for the Catnip language.
Built with ratatui, it provides syntax highlighting, fish-like autosuggestions,
and tab completion.
.PP
The REPL can also be launched via
.B catnip repl
or simply
.B catnip
with no arguments.
.SH ENVIRONMENT
.TP
.B CATNIP_OPTIMIZE
Comma-separated optimization flags (e.g. \fBjit,tco:on\fR).
.TP
.B CATNIP_CACHE
Cache control (\fBon\fR, \fBoff\fR).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR catnip (1),
.BR catnip-lsp (1)
.SH AUTHOR
Aristofor Kolomb <aristofor@gmail.com>
